    "1203810": {
        "Desc": "Keep following the scent and looking for clues",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I—It's..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Agh! Look at this red stuff... Wh—What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "By the looks of it, a letter, written on a piece of torn clothing. The ink is bone-dry... it must have been written quite some time ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Well, let's take a look."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Mm-hmm..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "According to this letter, a conflict arose because Amenoma Yuuya wanted to seize a blade belonging to Mr. Nagato."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Yuuya started the fire that destroyed the warehouse, and wounded Mr. Nagato in the fight. Mr. Nagato kept chase as long as he could, eventually stopping here to write this letter when his strength gave out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... where is he...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "He was not only mortally wounded, but also under the heavy influence of Tatarigami. Add to that the fact that its aura seems to have attracted a horde of monsters, and... I'm afraid he may no longer be with us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Whatever traces there may have been of his fate beyond after this point, they've since been disturbed by the hilichurls. There's nothing more for us to find here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's ask the Tenryou Commission to do a thorough search later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There are more important things right now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "Yes, right now, we need to uncover some more important truths."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "If Amenoma Yuuya is attacking other people indiscriminately, then the longer we take to find him, the more people risk meeting the same tragic end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Right, so let's get moving!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How did it come to this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's not in his nature."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I wouldn't be surprised if he, too, fell prey to the influence of the Tatarigami."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "For a practitioner of the martial arts, the easiest desire to inflame would be their pursuit of further power and skill."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "All the clues that at first seemed disparate and disconnected... it seems that now we know the thread that runs between them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I have a hypothesis that, if it's correct, not only explains the series of events leading to the two men's disappearance, but also zeroes in on the attacker's identity."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Wait, you've figured it out? So these two cases are connected after all?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "I believe so... but it's something of an outlandish idea. I will only be able to confirm my suspicions once we've met him in person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaedehara Kazuha",
                    "T": "On with the search. We must stay vigilant. At any point now, we may find ourselves in danger."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
